Package schema2template.template

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileCreationListEntry
    Is created by FileCreationListHandler.
    FileCreationListHandler
    If a Velocity template should be used multiple times (e.g. for every element of the schema), For every file to be created we create a line in the file-creation-list.
    GrammarAdditionsFileHandler
    Often Process the custom configuration data XML Reads only the grammar-additions.xml Handler for existing grammar-additions.xml
    SourceCodeBaseClass
    This calss encapsulates the name of the java base class, which is a Java super class where shared attributes and elements are being moved to.
    SourceCodeModel
    Model for Java specific enhancements like common base classes for elements and Java value types for value types used in schema.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileCreationListEntry.EntryType
    Type of file-creation-list entry (file or path)
